309
00:14:30,619 --> 00:14:32,318
Pass them to me.

310
00:14:33,828 --> 00:14:35,688
Hey, it's coming off so easily!

311
00:14:37,498 --> 00:14:38,698
You don't have to scrub hard.

312
00:14:38,798 --> 00:14:40,998
