393
00:18:17,278 --> 00:18:19,948
(P Fish and Chips)

394
00:18:20,148 --> 00:18:23,858
(P Fish and Chips)

395
00:18:24,188 --> 00:18:25,218
I see...

396
00:18:25,918 --> 00:18:28,328
(All of them earned more than our restaurant.)

397
00:18:29,258 --> 00:18:31,527
