425
00:19:45,798 --> 00:19:48,508
We have 1,250 dollars? Is it 1,250 to 1,300?

426
00:19:49,238 --> 00:19:50,914
- I will calculate.
- Did we make it halfway at least?

427
00:19:50,938 --> 00:19:52,138
Not even half?

428
00:19:52,508 --> 00:19:55,978
